The paper discusses the use of deep convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for insect monitoring, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes the use of one-class classifiers, which are a type of machine learning algorithm, indicating the relevance of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
